{"tid":1603013,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"「軍師」問題在於無小隊，個個都係散兵，無反速龍小隊，無神獸隊，五十人向前衝已經效果好大","createTime":"2019-09-29T14:51:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T16:53:30.000Z","uid":126621,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"39d124df3287334083e061362be5ae3ea6c3c263","tid":1603013,"uid":126621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T14:51:34.000Z","msg":"如果組成到三個隊伍<br />\n每隊50個人 分左中右<br />\n150個真勇士不逃難<br />\n(唔代表唔撤退）<br />\n每個都守望相助嘅話<br />\n我相信後面嘅和理非都唔會走得咁肉酸<br />\n而前面都可以有好多戰術<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n等睇人屌我冷氣軍師收皮啦"},{"pid":"a688b793b16ca723d0a738d7eae19cd2f83b2e94","tid":1603013,"uid":104811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T14:51:49.000Z","msg":"聽日 930 全港三罷"},{"pid":"ce707047ce982c10cbf4b62e7740fe974ee28426","tid":1603013,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T14:52:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8b0c2e89d56bd424879d85d758dc1d406c16b87e","tid":1603013,"uid":166129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T16:34:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79c26cefd04aa3cefdcb9d66a8a7ed975ce552e0","tid":1603013,"uid":67553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T16:36:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24dd8f2e66fddb61b0039df4a43c9177a99f208b","tid":1603013,"uid":110851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T16:53:30.000Z","msg":"同意<br />\n幫推"}]}